Package: indiamart-scraper
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6, libgl1, libxcb1, libxkbcommon-x11-0, libxcb-cursor0, libxcb-icccm4, libxcb-image0, libxcb-keysyms1, libxcb-randr0, libxcb-render-util0, libxcb-shape0, libxcb-shm0, libxcb-sync1, libxcb-xfixes0, libxcb-xinerama0, libxcb-xinput0, libegl1, libnss3, libnspr4, libdbus-1-3, libfontconfig1, libxrandr2, libasound2
Maintainer: IndiaMART Scraper Maintainer <support@codeberg.org>
Description: Native desktop application for IndiaMART lead scraping.
 This application packages the lead scraper into a native desktop experience with
 embedded browser dashboard, real-time activity log, safety constraints, and
 database export tools. Runs completely offline without external terminal launch.
